Kenneth Robert BOEHM, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Marie STEPHENSON, et al., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-0184 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. February 23, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The parties' stipulation for dismissal filed February 20, 2018, is treated as a notice of voluntary dismissal and is granted. This appeal is dismissed.
